When I watch a series on my PC and suddenly it turns off because I no longer have battery.
My stomach empties after I poop, then I feel alone but it's especially during vacations but it's not the case for this, it doesn't count much.
When you go up to get something, you forget it on the way, you come down and when you get to the bottom you remember so you have to go up again.
When someone asks you the same thing, several times throughout the day.



Why do we love to hate, to revolt? why is it that it...




It comes to me when I have something to say and two seconds later I forget it <<<<<<<<<<


It is annoying when people try to contradict me when I am right.
When I am at McDonald's and someone takes 20 minutes to order a salad or an ice cream. I am like: WWW53

When I say "good day" to someone and this person responds "good evening"
When I see that FDP bird that doesn't know how to fly on the ground.
When I want to participate and the teacher takes so much time before asking me that I forget what I wanted to say

When someone tells you "I have to tell you something important!", you tell them to say it, and they respond "I'll tell you later"
I hate you when I see your face.




It's gone when you speak well with someone and the next day, nothing.
When I'm busy, I don't have messages, snaps, or notifications, and when I'm free, there are too many messages, snaps, and notifications.

When I listen to a song on my phone, someone decides to talk to me
They ignore you when people don't respond to texts even though you see them all the time on their phones.
When we have all put away our things, closed our bags and put the chairs on the tables, the teacher says "get out your agendas"...



When I brush my teeth with toothpaste under water and the toothpaste falls into the sink :(

When you give a nickname to a friend, and everyone calls them that way after...

When I wake up one minute before the alarm rings


When books don't close properly. I never knew how to fix it... WWW60


When the bell rings to say that the class is over, it rings, and the teacher keeps you for a while longer to finish the class.


When I tweet a perfect tweet and someone else retweets the same tweet and it has 28,738,292 retweets

It hurts when my dreams are shattered in 2 seconds.
When I feel like vomiting but it happens... WWW62
It comes when I am cut when I speak






